from erppeek import Client
c = Client('http://localhost:8069', 'abenergia', 'gisce')
contracts = ['2019007','2012109','2002855','2002859','2018957','2018850','2018889','2018975','2018927','2018966','2018974','2019003','2018992','2018994','2019103','2019008','10439','2018888','2019121','2018965','2016505','2019101','2018998','2004027','2019001','2019026','2019106','2018948','2017291','2019057','2018944','2018915','2019076','2002853','2019113','2019104','2019013','2018916','2018964','2002861','2002857','2018110','2019014','2019100','2019083','2019047','2019033','2018931','2018943','2004732','2002856','2017551','2018856','2018955','2002847','2016859','1003038','2002854','2019084','2002845','2002858','2018993','2018857','2012571','2013196','2019095','2019102','2018918','2002850','2018852','2018981','2002860','1010128','2018935','2019051','2019110','2019087','2012108','2019031','2002851','2002849','2002852','2002862','2019089','2016750','9751','2019044','2016070','2019009','2018921','2018953','2019111','2018952','2018989','2019016','10590','2018951','2019081','2015832','2019021','2019022','2018945','2018963','2019126','2018663','2019043','2019097','2019109','2019045','2007572','2002844','1023325','2019025','2019032','2018991','2003145','2018545','2018979','2018309','2018999','2016860','2018687','2018969','2019105','2018664','2002848','2018980','2018930','2019054','2019086','2019096','2012379','2016476','2018960']
pol_ids = c.GiscedataPolissa.search([('name','in',contracts)], context={'active_test':False})
print(len(pol_ids))
vals = {'tipus_renovacio': 'tacita'}
from tqdm import tqdm
for x in tqdm(range(11)):
    pol_ids_act = pol_ids[len(pol_ids)/10*x:len(pol_ids)/10*(x+1)]
    c.GiscedataPolissa.write(pol_ids_act, vals)
    print(len(pol_ids_act))
